prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor painting of a humorous birthday card front cover. A cartoon illustrated version of the man from the reference photo [497f9234-09d6-464c-9f43-432b344fa5d3], capturing his distinct features, glasses, dark hair, and smiling expression, is shown comically struggling to blow out a single, very stubborn, magically re-lighting birthday candle on a tiny cupcake he's holding. Puffs of exaggerated cartoon smoke come from his mouth. The scene is lighthearted and funny. In the center, the elegant handwritten cursive script text "Happy Birthday" is beautifully integrated. The artwork has soft flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, visible paper texture, and organic watercolor paint bleeds along the edges, on a clean white background.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
